      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAYKAYANN (3) won first up for the first time then raced on the speed last time but was overhauled and finished seventh over 2000m at Pakenham. Stayed at the same trip last time and ready for this distance now. UNSEEN RULER (1) was below his best last time, finishing sixth and beaten 5.5 lengths over 2400m at Sandown-Hillside. Good effort the start prior in the Warrnambool Cup, which is a better form reference for this. EL JAMES (2) continues to race well with a win two back at Warrnambool before finishing 1.75 lengths away in third last time over 2000m at Casterton. The winkers have been removed for this and expected to be in the finish. LODBROK (5) should be nearing peak fitness and suited back up to this trip.",
